[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "シトリン、食器洗いを手伝いましょう！\n料理とは片付けまで含めてですから――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_038_00038",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "はいはい。あーあ、やろうと思ってたのに\nなんか急にやる気なくなってきたな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00039",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "まったく、食べ終わっても賑やかだこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00040",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "聞いたぜ。この人数の家族をまとめ上げて\n宴会やったんだってな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00041",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ん、まあね。ヘルトのこともあったし……\nそれに、兄弟でまた揉めるのはごめんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00042",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "そうだな。家族仲良しでいられたら、\nそれが一番だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00043",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "しかし家族会を開いたり、お前も成長したもんだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00044",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "へへ、どーもぉ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00045",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "いいかい、しつこい汚れを落とすにはコツがあるんだ。\nこうやってね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_038_00046",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "わ、すごい……！\nイェルカ姉貴、なんでも知ってるね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_038_00047",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なんかね、こうして九偉人みんなで過ごすの、\n初めてのことじゃない気がするの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00048",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "記憶にはないんだけど、これと似たようなことが\n前にもあったような……みたいな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00049",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "思い出せそうで思い出せない……\nあとちょっとなんだけど。もどかしいなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00050",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "そうか。そこまで記憶の蓋が開きかけてるのなら\nきっと何かのきっかけで思い出せるさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00051",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ん、だといいけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00052",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "大丈夫だって。お前はあれだろ？\n伝説の九偉人の一人なんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00053",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "九偉人と記憶が戻ることには関係がないと思うけど？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00054",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "そりゃそうなんだが……大した奴なんだから、\n記憶だってわけなく戻っちまうさって言いてえんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00055",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "励ますのへったくそね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00056",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "るせぇ、海の男は背中で語るんだよ。\nこういうのは向いてねえんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00057",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "まあ、その、あれだ。お前が大した奴で\n九偉人の一人だったとしてもだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00058",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "俺もフロッケもハイディも、お前のこと\n家族だって思ってっからよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00059",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なに、どうしたの？　娘を嫁に出す親父の気分？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00060",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "お前なあ、茶化すなっての。俺は結構真剣に……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00061",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "大丈夫よ、多分。兄弟と仲良くなっても\n記憶が完全に戻ったとしても……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00062",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私が帰る家は、ここだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00063",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]